@startuml
title DevLink - Adapter (wzorzec strukturalny)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

class "CLI Daemon" as Daemon {
  +run_task(client, task_payload)
}

interface AgentAdapter {
  +run(task: AgentTask): AsyncIterator<AgentEvent>
}

class CodexAdapter {
  -stdout_lines: list
  -stderr_lines: list
  -assistant_messages: list
  -edited_files: list
  +run(task: AgentTask): AsyncIterator<AgentEvent>
}

class ShellAdapter {
  +run(task: AgentTask): AsyncIterator<AgentEvent>
}

class AgentTask {
  +id: str
  +prompt: str
  +project_path: str
  +model: str
  +approval_policy: str
}

class AgentEvent {
  +event_type: str
  +message: str
  +payload: dict
}

class "Codex CLI process" as CodexProcess {
  +codex exec --json
  +stdout
  +stderr
  +exit_code
}

class "Backend API" as BackendApi {
  +POST /api/cli/tasks/{id}/events/
  +PATCH /api/cli/tasks/{id}/
}

Daemon --> AgentAdapter : uses common contract
Daemon --> BackendApi : sends AgentEvent

CodexAdapter ..|> AgentAdapter
ShellAdapter ..|> AgentAdapter

CodexAdapter --> CodexProcess : adapts external output
CodexAdapter --> AgentEvent : emits normalized events
ShellAdapter --> AgentEvent : emits normalized events

AgentAdapter --> AgentTask : consumes
AgentAdapter --> AgentEvent : produces

note right of CodexAdapter
Adapter zamienia stdout/stderr
i JSON stream z Codex CLI
na wspolny format AgentEvent.
end note

@enduml

